{"word":"ἀγχίστροφος","slug":"ἀγχίστροφος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγχίστροφος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:στρέφω'><el>στρέφω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>turning closely, quick-wheeling</i>, of a hawk, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>quick-changing, sudden</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <i>suddenly</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}